         <notesStmt>
            <note type="summary">Z.s reply to wedding invitation. On the secret of
                            Birkat ha-Kiddushin. On the Kavvanah "Harei at meḳudeshet li", secret of
                            Ḥuppah, Kavvanah of the seven blessings, Kavvanah whilst drinking the
                            wine, preparation for intercourse, prohibition of candlelight, prayer of
                            virgin men is not prayed, times of forbidden intercourse, permitted on
                            the night of ritual purification, so also Ḥol ha-Moed and when Passover
                            falls on Shabbat.</note>
            <note type="incipit" xml:lang="he">הרצים יצאו תכופים
                        באמרי</note>
